## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **tisagenlecleucel Kymriah 2017** = first CAR-T globally — CD19 pediatric/AYA B-ALL paradigm-creating. "living drug" lexicon coining + autologous manufacturing complexity 정립.
2. **axi-cel + brexu-cel + liso-cel + ide-cel + cilta-cel 2017-2022** = CAR-T 5-product 첫 5년 — CD19 + BCMA dual-target dominance. Carvykti (cilta-cel) 2022 deeper response R/R MM 가 BCMA next-gen 정점.
3. **afami-cel Adaptimmune 2024** = first FDA TCR-T — synovial sarcoma + MAGE-A4. HLA-A*02:01 restriction = patient stratification 구조적 한계 (50% 인구 only). solid tumor TCR-T 의 entry.
4. **lifileucel Amtagvi Iovance 2024** = first FDA TIL — advanced melanoma post-checkpoint. autologous tumor 절제 + ex-vivo expansion 4-6 weeks. solid tumor cell therapy 의 비-engineered approach.
5. **tabelecleucel Ebvallo Atara 2022** = first FDA off-the-shelf allogeneic — EBV-CTL post-transplant LPD. HLA-restricted donor selection + T-cell receptor native (engineered 아님).
6. **remestemcel-L Ryoncil Mesoblast 2024** = first FDA MSC — pediatric SR-aGvHD. 15+ years 임상 후 첫 FDA MSC. mechanism = paracrine immunomodulation (IDO + PGE2 + TGF-β).
7. **CRS (cytokine release syndrome) + ICANS** grade 1-4 — tocilizumab IL-6 + corticosteroid IV dexamethasone. 2024 tisa-cel + axi-cel + ide-cel + cilta-cel + brexu-cel secondary T-cell malig FDA black-box = persistence-driven long-term safety signal.
8. **allogeneic CAR-T (universal)** — TCR knockout (GvHD 예방) + B2M knockout (HLA class I 회피) + HLA-A knockout. Allogene + Caribou + CRISPR Therapeutics + Cellectis paradigm. 2025 첫 FDA approval 예상.
9. **iPSC-derived (Fate FT819 + FT500 + Vertex VX-880 + BlueRock OpCT001)** — pluripotent → terminal differentiation 의 universal donor. functional cure paradigm — T1DM (Vertex) + Parkinson (BlueRock) + cardiac iPSC-CM. cross-disease.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, $400-500K pricing + community center expansion + 한국 K-CAR-T (Kymriah 2022 식약처 + 안트로젠 + 큐로셀 임상) 같은 access policy 한정.

